data.text: Nyasaye e kar pondowa kendo tekowa,
Kata obedoni pige manie nam wuo kendo golo buoyo
Nitie aora moro ma pige kelo mor e dala Nyasaye,
Nyasaye odak e iye omiyo ok obi podho;
Ogendini nigi chandruok, kendo pinjeruodhi podho;
Omiyo lwenje rumo e tungʼ piny koni gi koni;
“Bed mos, kendo ngʼe ni an Nyasaye;
